data.description: Nestled among the trees with your own hillside privacy in a natural terrain setting on over 1 acre of land. Terrific opportunity to move right in and make your own custom upgrades to this stylish contemporary home!   2 kitchens, perfect for mother-in-law suite or extended family!  Sunroom off kitchen & family room.  double fireplace, Wooded setting and a great location within 10 min. of Downtown Huntsville Hospital, Parkway Place Mall, and other shopping or professional services. Many other upscale homes in this SE Huntsville location.  Don't miss this one!!
